item.title: You Won't Believe What Everglow just did with 'How You Like That' - You Have to See it to Believe it!
item.description: You Won’t Believe What Everglow Just Did with ‘How You Like That’ Everglow is an up and coming K-pop girl group that has been gaining a lot of attention They recently released their latest single, ‘How You Like That’, and it has been a huge hit Now, they have just released their performance video for the song and it is something you have to see to believe Who is Everglow? Everglow is a six-member girl group under Yuehua Entertainment.
